OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright or sunny spells and a
OL,6,Ffew scattered showers, these more
OL,7,Ffrequent in the far northwest. Fewer
OL,8,Fshowers and more in the way of
OL,9,Fsunshine for the south and east of
OL,10,FHighland. Rather cool, breezy in north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,13,Fsunny then clear interludes and a few
OL,14,Fshowers, these showers more
OL,15,Fconcentrated in the Northwest and
OL,16,FIsles, fewer in south and east.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FA mostly dry day with bright
OL,19,Fspells the best sunshine around the
OL,20,Fcoasts. Still the odd passing shower.
OL,21,FRather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
