OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fstarting bright then cloudy with rain
OL,7,Fin the afternoon. Sunny spells on
OL,8,FMonday then some light rain later.
OL,9,FTuesday breezy with showers and sunny
OL,10,Fintervals.
